 Edges#{1}":[55,65],"#Voice Agents#Related Skills":[66,69],"#Voice Agents#Related Skills#{1}":[68,69]},"outlinks":[],"metadata":{"name":"voice-agents","description":"Voice agents represent the frontier of AI interaction - humans speaking naturally with AI systems. The challenge isn't just speech recognition and synthesis, it's achieving natural conversation flow with sub-800ms latency while handling interruptions, background noise, and emotional nuance.  This skill covers two architectures: speech-to-speech (OpenAI Realtime API, lowest latency, most natural) and pipeline (STT→LLM→TTS, more control, easier to debug). Key insight: latency is the constraint. Hu","source":"vibeship-spawner-skills (Apache 2.0)"},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"00_System/Links/App_agent_skills_repo/voice-agents/SKILL.md"},
